Package: DMRcate
Title: Illumina 450K methylation array spatial analysis methods
Version: 0.99.11
Date: 2014-26-03
Author: Tim Peters
Maintainer: Tim Peters <Tim.Peters@csiro.au>
Description: De novo identification and extraction of differentially methylated regions (DMRs) in the human genome using Illumina Infinium HumanMethylation450 BeadChip array data. Provides functionality for filtering probes possibly confounded by SNPs and cross-hybridisation. Includes bedGraph and plotting functions.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.2), ks, limma, minfi, DMRcatedata
biocViews: DifferentialMethylation, IlluminaChip, Preprocessing, SNP
Suggests: knitr, RUnit, BiocGenerics,
        IlluminaHumanMethylation450kanno.ilmn12.hg19
Imports: methods, graphics
License: GPL-3
VignetteBuilder: knitr

